&lt;h2 id="how-to-choose-the-right-ai-tool-for-your-business"&gt;How to Choose the Right AI Tool for Your Business&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choosing the right AI tool depends on your specific business needs and goals. Here’s a simple decision-making tree to guide you through the process:&lt;/p&gt;
